author: ehillenius
msg: remove check on <a. An example of where this check is wrong is with a stylesheet <link used in <wicket:link> tags. If that cannot be resolved, an ExternalLink is created, which then failed when rendering because it is not a <a. Furthermore, I see no reason why ExternalLink couldn't be used with <link directly when people wish to do so.
